title: Ep. 107 "Hoe Baths"
description: Duck butter, hairy backs, sour smells from down below... this week we talk about hygiene and maintenance. Whether you've been there, or had to tell someone they were there, we all know how awkward the hygiene convo can be.  Especially with someone you're sleeping with.
